        <mxCell id="P1" value="&lt;b&gt;Problem 1: Target-set mismatch&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;s' ∉ reachable set S_codec&lt;br&gt;Ranking vs s' ≠ ranking vs D(Q(E(s')))&lt;br&gt;→ &lt;font color=&quot;#b85450&quot;&gt;biased group rewards for GRPO&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;spacingLeft=10;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=6;" vertex="1" parent="1">
