        <mxCell id="CAP" value="Figure 1. RC-GRPO vs. existing GRPO post-training. Left: scoring candidates against raw frames (target-set mismatch) and broadcasting one sequence-level advantage mis-specify GRPO's rewards R and advantages A. Right: (1) rank w.r.t. reachable reconstructions s̃'=D(Q(E(s'))); (2) project updates to preserve raw first-order progress; (3) assign per-frame-block advantages from return-to-go. Final metrics remain vs. raw s'. Backbone, tokenizer, and decoder stay frozen." style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;spacingTop=4;" vertex="1" parent="1">
